# IEP Azure Resource Planning List
This list of resources is based off of the list originally described in the Milestone 2 RFP.
## In-scope resources for consideration

| Resource | Resource provider |
|---|---|
| Virtual Network | `Microsoft.Network` |
| Subnets | `Microsoft.Network` |
| Network Security Groups | `Microsoft.Network` |
| Route Tables | `Microsoft.Network` |
| Private Endpoints | `Microsoft.Network` |
| Application Gateway | `Microsoft.Network` |
| WAF Policy for Application Gateway | `Microsoft.Network` |
| Private DNS zone / private DNS networking objects | `Microsoft.Network` |
| Load Balancer | `Microsoft.Network` |
| API Management | `Microsoft.ApiManagement` |
| App Service Environment | `Microsoft.Web` |
| App Service Plan | `Microsoft.Web` |
| App Service / Web App / API App | `Microsoft.Web` |
| Azure Functions / Function App | `Microsoft.Web` |
| Azure Container Registry | `Microsoft.ContainerRegistry` |
| Azure Data Factory | `Microsoft.DataFactory` |
| Service Bus | `Microsoft.ServiceBus` |
| Event Grid | `Microsoft.EventGrid` |
| Azure Database for PostgreSQL | `Microsoft.DBforPostgreSQL` |
| Storage Account | `Microsoft.Storage` |
| Log Analytics Workspace | `Microsoft.OperationalInsights` |
| Application Insights | `Microsoft.Insights` |
| Azure Monitor alerting / monitor resources | `Microsoft.Insights` / `Microsoft.Monitor` / `Microsoft.AlertsManagement` |
| Key Vault | `Microsoft.KeyVault` |
| Managed Identity | `Microsoft.ManagedIdentity` |
| Azure Automation / Runbooks | `Microsoft.Automation` |
| Logic Apps | `Microsoft.Logic` |
| Azure Cache for Redis | `Microsoft.Cache` |
| Cosmos DB | `Microsoft.DocumentDB` |

